This paper primarily focuses on the impact of ad-blockers and anti-ad-blockers on online businesses and user experience, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses data collection and analysis, which can be categorized under social and information networks (cs.SI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper touches upon legal and ethical issues related to ad-blockers and anti-ad-blockers, which can be classified under computers and society (cs.CY).
